{"tid":2275434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣西南寧動物園被爆疑似虐畜，老虎飢瘦如柴、迫殘疾海豚表演","createTime":"2020-11-07T07:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T08:28:58.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7654322c86b265ce4bcd35c459ce76d886246fa5","tid":2275434,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"最近廣西南寧動物動圓被曝疑似虐畜，有不少遊客指園內動物毫無精神，老虎飢瘦如柴，質疑動物園虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hiL2LNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiL2LNz.jpg&h=89754f3e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有遊客發現廣州動物園內有老虎瘦得只剩下皮包骨，而且還會吃樹皮、吃草。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xham1k3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXham1k3.jpg&h=6fee31f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有蘇卡達象龜背上被掛上國旗和錢箱，供遊客丟零錢，而且遊客指養殖象龜的池子非常污糟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3TLJz3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3TLJz3.jpg&h=faa73b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻係之前在野外救援的中華白海豚，被安排放在動物園醫治，但園方醫好傷後不放歸，留在動物園做動物表演，最後導致吻部斷裂，但園方依舊繼續安排牠表演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gRdSwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gRdSwU.jpg&h=e2210ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2kx75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2kx75f.jpg&h=e910666a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZHwEbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZHwEbV.png&h=551651aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有遊客貼出以前去動物園的相片，指出以往都曾經懷疑園方裡動物的健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRAaUNy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRAaUNy.png&h=0b3931c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n對此，動物園回應指該老虎天生苗條清瘦，並解釋因為係高度親近交配繁衍下一代，所以相對瘦小很多。園區工作人員也表示，華南虎的飲食要求比運動員還要高，吃草有助於老虎消化。動物園表示將在老虎區周邊明顯位置張貼關於華南虎的宣傳資料，免得大家繼續誤會。<br />\n<br />\n至於，有關殘疾海豚一事，廣西漁政部門表示已介入調查，暫時未有結果。"},{"pid":"e5082ea4be90cec78f074f283e0fb5cec4e8dfe8","tid":2275434,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"咁即係廣西定廣州呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf94cc9d779dc20c0fe71c22b4b3e27188c8452","tid":2275434,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"又廣西又廣州？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8f6ac3310ab73d1369efa06e54f89d626d2be0","tid":2275434,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"做支那人慘啲定做支那動物園啲動物慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c39fabe47d7fe1cc1adbef5df8bd9e634b090a3","tid":2275434,"uid":54431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:57.000Z","msg":"老虎食草 有助消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b62001cbcbfd80f3fe51d87d15d83eba023377","tid":2275434,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"烏龜都要愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24459c4e857aa70f80c1b5aef64f36db7199f6f8","tid":2275434,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5082ea4be90cec78f074f283e0fb5cec4e8dfe8","tid":2275434,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"咁即係廣西定廣州呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"柒咗 睇錯 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似應該要分返開<br />\n老虎係廣洲動物園<br />\n海豚係南寧動物園<br />\n因為兩單新閒都係近期，上面啲人溝埋一齊講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b70c76b0b029cd3abc06bedd25009d87b2a6ce","tid":2275434,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf94cc9d779dc20c0fe71c22b4b3e27188c8452","tid":2275434,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"又廣西又廣州？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75621b567b8acafc6bc3cdc16daa14de300b1b1b","tid":2275434,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c39fabe47d7fe1cc1adbef5df8bd9e634b090a3","tid":2275434,"uid":54431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:57.000Z","msg":"老虎食草 有助消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:17:53.000Z","msg":"老虎信咗佛"},{"pid":"7813b318845173287acb5df0e20173b77f08f901","tid":2275434,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8f6ac3310ab73d1369efa06e54f89d626d2be0","tid":2275434,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"做支那人慘啲定做支那動物園啲動物慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"咪又係喺個籠度"},{"pid":"e21af2dd910426a7d9f61d6ca21f09fc2e9a921d","tid":2275434,"uid":189453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"突然諗起尋日定前日 講話韓國女團徒手摸熊貓係辱華<br />\n吹到中國對動物幾好幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\